## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `npm run audit:security`: Verify the security scan passes with the corrected path.
- `npm run audit:svelte`: Verify Svelte 4 violations check.
- `npm run verify`: Execute the full evaluation sequence (audit, lint, test) to ensure 100% purity.
- `npm test`: Run unit tests (Vitest) to ensure no regressions in core logic.

### Manual Verification
- Inspect the terminal output of `npm run verify` to confirm all 176+ tests pass and audits are clean.
